  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049910/extras/04b9f30d4017b13784da831a964c1f04.avif?t=1729858276\" width=600 height=238 /></span><br>Runny Bunny is an arcade game where you control a little bunny that must collect all the dots and carrots to unlock the passage to the next level. With each level, the complexity increases and new mechanics are introduced.<br><br><strong>⮞ Collect all to unlock the passage</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049910/extras/1374122bc685aaaaa70341ba8db15ad7.poster.avif?t=1729858276\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049910/extras/1374122bc685aaaaa70341ba8db15ad7.webm?t=1729858276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049910/extras/1374122bc685aaaaa70341ba8db15ad7.mp4?t=1729858276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>⮞ Beware of Traps!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049910/extras/0afd96e2febf7e54d906814431d4ab2a.poster.avif?t=1729858276\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049910/extras/0afd96e2febf7e54d906814431d4ab2a.webm?t=1729858276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049910/extras/0afd96e2febf7e54d906814431d4ab2a.mp4?t=1729858276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>⮞ Move quickly and dodge enemies</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.ste